metadata.name: 𝔎𝔫𝔞𝔳𝔢
metadata.description:
Knave is a heavy metal band formed by guitarist/lead vocalist Evan and bassist/backing vocalist Mason. They, later on, completed the band lineup when drummer Jack and keyboardist Lilith join them.

Knave firstly becomes well known for its aggressive fast-paced music style, or "thrash metal." Then, they started adopting different genres such as nu-metal, deathcore, and rock. Sometimes, they even experiment with a more pop-rock music style.

- Evan Volkov -
